            <p>St. Mary's School, Bannerghatta nestled in the vicinity of Bangalore is a part of the st. mary's Group of Institutions. 
                            In its continual efforts to revolutionize the education scenario guided by the futuristic view of Dr. Augustine F. Pinto, Founder Chairman of Ryan Group. 
                            It is a co-educational school affiliated to C.B.S.E with the state-of-the-art infrastructure.</p>

<p>Our effort is directed towards global education integrated with innovative use of technology to develop global 
    citizens through a holistic approach.</p>
<p>  It is our mission to facilitate:</p>

<p> 1.The development of global citizens - individuals with self-confidence who are able to contribute to community life, build tolerance & accountability and able to deal with emotional and spiritual quotients.</p>

<p>2.A student with knowledge, attitude, skills, social and moral values which enhances their personality development, physical and psycho-social capabilities which are effectively achieved through professional coaching in sports, creative and personality enhancement activities.</p>

<p>3.The delivery of curriculum by incorporating activities based on the Multiple Intelligences theory of Howard Gardner, professor at Harvard University that leads to literacy, inquiry, creativity, and critical thinking.</p>

